Class ElementWriter

java.lang.Object
io.github.eutro.jwasm.BaseVisitor<ElementVisitor>
io.github.eutro.jwasm.ElementVisitor
io.github.eutro.jwasm.ElementWriter
All Implemented Interfaces:
ByteArrayConvertible
public class ElementWriter extends ElementVisitor implements ByteArrayConvertible
A DataVisitor that generates the corresponding WebAssembly bytecode as it is visited. This can be retrieved using toByteArray() after visitEnd().
